overview: BusyTrade is a global B2B business and B2B manufacturer directory, founded in 1999, BusyTrade is one of the most popular B2B trade leads, B2B sales, B2B marketing and B2B information platform for global importer and exporters to do business online. With over 3 Million members coming from over 200 countries, BusyTrade offers free buying leads, selling leads and wholesale product informations to its members, thus, BusyTrade is recognized as one of top5 B2B marketplaces on the B2B world. www.busytrade.com
